A simple app for tracking books and current reading progress.

Prerequisites:
* Docker - https://hub.docker.com/search/?type=edition&offering=community
* .NET 10 SDK -  https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download/dotnet/10.0
* .NET Aspire - https://aspire.dev

The app runs in .NET Aspire now, so all you need to do is run the AppHost project

```console
$ dotnet run --project ReadTrack.AppHost
```